reut2-008.sgm, MCDONALD'S &lt;MCD> UP ON REAFFIRMED RECOMMENDATION, McDonald's Corp rose sharply todayafter receiving a second recommendation in as many sessions,traders said.    Today, analyst Richard Simon of Goldman Sachs and Coreaffirmed his recommendation of the stock and put it on hisfocus list

